<TEXT>
marion barry told a grand jury last year his 
visits to the hotel room of a convicted drug dealer in 1988 were 
not unusual or criminal according to a taperecording of his 
testimony played today at the mayors cocaine possession and 
perjury trial 
his assertion contradicted the testimony last week of the 
