donald trumps bankers have approved a 30day 
20 million loan after agreeing in principle to a bigger longterm 
financial rescue for the cashstrapped developer a source said 
today 
an immediate 20 million cash infusion will enable trump to make 
necessary bond payments while finishing touches are placed on a 
complex 65 million bailout a participant in the negotiations said 
