a plutoniumpowered satellite that 
will be launched from the shuttle discovery this fall to explore 
the suns poles poses little health risk in the event of an 
accident space officials said tuesday 
we have looked at the statistics and our conclusion is 
that we think its definitely as safe as it can be and were not 
