of discoverys fiveman crew 
ulysses scientific instruments will be powered by one 
radioisotope thermoelectric generator rtg which converts heat 
from decaying plutonium into electricity two such generators were 
aboard the galileo spacecraft that was sent on a sixyear journey 
to jupiter from the shuttle atlantis last october 
