will eventually lead to even greater adjustments in the program 
the sugar program is bitterly opposed by manufacturers of candy 
baked goods soft drinks and other sweets because it prevents 
cheaper worldpriced sugar from being sold in the united states 
in defense of government sugar support house agriculture sugar 
subcommittee chairman jerry huckaby dla said it keeps prices 
