10 and bill cosbys new ghost dad generally seem to use 
the whole range of instruments and have a rich natural 
nonsynthesized sound 
it may therefore sadden foes of computer music to learn that 
mancini the graduate of big bands uses synthesizers 
ive been using them almost since the first time they came 
out in one way or another he says they get interesting 
sounds and they get better and better i use them in conjunction 
with an acoustic orchestra 
heresy no says the composer i just think they give you a 
much bigger palette to work from 
