any kind of lie rca marti jones 
 
john hiatt elvis costello marshall crenshaw janis ian the 
list of songwriters ohio singer marti jones has tapped in her 
career is long and impressive 
on her new album the popcountry singer and her husband don 
dixon decide to do most of the writing the results coming off of 
