for several months to acquire 70 airbus industrie a320s but will 
not complete the deal without concessions hoar said 
twa also has talked with mcdonnell douglas corp and several 
leasing companies about adding more md80s to its fleet and has 
determined that some jets will be available within a few months he 
said 
hoar also said twa was looking at other possibilities for 
strengthening its competitive position including building or 
buying a hub in the eastern united states merging with another 
airline or buying another airline adding domestic and 
international flights from st louis and expanding into the soviet 
union eastern europe and the pacific 
